    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと……\n狭いんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously…\nIt’s getting cramped in here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.7666666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "一気に……増えたな\n寮にこんなに人数が入るのは、初めてかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Numbers did increase overnight.\nI don’t think the dorm has ever been this full before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.466666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "洗った洗濯物は各自で自分の部屋に持っていくように\n言ったはずです。これは誰のですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn’t I tell everyone to take their clean laundry back to their room?\nWhose is this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "それって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 17.46666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、そこにいるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s {user}’s. He’s right there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.500000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.500000000000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "もう、自分のなら自分のって先に言ってください",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it was yours‚ then why didn’t you say so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "それより……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.48952376047771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（――話題を変えたいのか、雫は千紗の方をチラリと見る）\n（千紗は促されて、恥ずかしそうに話し始める）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Shizuku glances at Chisa as if wanting to change the subject.）\n（Prompted by Shizuku‚ Chisa begins speaking shyly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの……\nこの寮、音……結構します……よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-um…\nThis dorm makes a lot of noise… doesn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.22759637037913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "音？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Noise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい\n夜中に、ミシミシとか……窓がガタっとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nI hear creaking at night… and the windows rattle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.62759637037912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、うん\nたまに聞こえるよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ yeah.\nI hear it‚ too‚ sometimes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.860929703712465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "木造だからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s probably the wooden structure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.66092970371246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？\n私、幽霊じゃないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?\nI thought it might be ghosts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.44448974132538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなもの、いる訳ないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what are you talking about? Ghosts aren’t real.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.27782307465871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.40283451875051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ……違うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ um… That’s not what I meant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.15505669911703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい\n琴乃ちゃん、怒っている訳じゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry~\nKotono isn’t upset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.86863942146303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、小さい頃から\n怪談話とかちょっと苦手だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s just that ever since she was small‚\nshe never liked ghost stories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.56863942146303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もしかして幽霊苦手……とか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ are you scared of ghosts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6353060881297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、そんなに嬉しそうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you look so happy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.86863942146302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "だって、琴乃ちゃんの意外な一面みたいなの\nあんまり知らなかったから……ふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m getting to see a side of you\nI didn’t know about before. Hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.57489800453187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "それで強く否定したんですね\nそうみたいよ、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why you are so sensitive.\nHear that‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.60823133786518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "うん……よかった\n琴乃ちゃんも、怖かったんだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I’m relieved.\nSo you were scared too‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8082313378652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、怖くなんか……！\nもう、渚",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m not scared!\nJeez‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.60823133786518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.17995795522415,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.333333333343,
          "startTime": 111.5132912885575
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 111.21329128855751
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 111.8132912885575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと……わ\nなんでみんな揃っているんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ excuse me!\nWhy is everyone gathered here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.37995795522421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "朝は、どうしてもこうなってしまうわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It always going to end up like this in the morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.81329128855756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それより、私の麻奈様のブルーレイがないのですけど\n誰か知りませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚ my Blu-ray of Mana-sama is missing.\nDoes anyone know where it is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.08467457408004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
